document.title: Circuit Breaker
document.description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in COMPONENT system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

2. Cap. Measurement

2. Trip Circuit

body.raw:
# Contactor

## Activities

1. Pickup-Dropout
2. Contact Resist.
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Mech. Endurance

## Activities

1. Ratio
2. Polarity Verif.
3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

2. Ins. Resist.
3. Mech. Interlock

body.raw:
# General

## Activities

1. Sec. Injection
2. Pri. Injection
3. Settings Verif.
4. Communication
5. Contact Resist.

document.description: Maintenance activities for Motor Prot. in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Motor Prot.

## Activities

1. Starting Time
2. Stall Prot.
3. Thermal OL
4. Unbal./Ph Loss

body.raw:
# Voltage Transformer

## Activities

1. Ratio
2. Polarity Verif.
3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

## Activities

1. Capacity Discharge
2. Voltage Stability
3. Float-Charge Efficiency
4. Ground Fault Detection

document.description: Maintenance activities for ACB in LV SWGR system

body.raw:
# ACB

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Trip Unit Cal.

## Activities

1. Cap. Measurement
2. Harm. Dist. Analysis
3. Switch. Transient
4. Ins. Resist.

document.description: Maintenance activities for Motor Control Center in LV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Motor Control Center

## Activities

1. Starter Cont. Op.
2. OL Relay Cal.
3. Phase Loss Det.

document.title: Circuit Breaker
document.description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

# Contactor

## Activities

1. Pickup-Dropout
2. Contact Resist.
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Mech. Endurance

# Directional OC

## Activities

1. Discrimination
2. Pickup
3. Timing

# MCB

## Activities

1. Trip Time SC-OL
2. Ins. Resist.
3. Mech. Operation

3. Thermal OL

document.description: Maintenance activities for Overcurrent in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Overcurrent

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Char. Curve
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Burden

document.description: Maintenance activities for Voltage Transformer in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Voltage Transformer

## Activities

1. Ratio
2. Polarity Verif.
3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

body.raw:
# Cooling System

## Activities

1. Pump-Fan Op.
2. Oil Flow Verif.
3. Temp. Control

2. Tight. Check
3. Polarity Verif.

document.title: Power Transformer
document.description: Maintenance activities for Power Transformer in POWER TRAFO system

body.raw:
# Power Transformer

## Activities

1. Ins. Resist.
2. Wind. Resist.
3. Turns Ratio
4. Mag. Current
5. Dielec. Absorp.
6. Diss. Gas Analysis
7. Sweep Freq. Resp.

## Activities

1. Buchholz Alarm
2. Press. Relief 
3. Wind. Temp. Alarm

document.description: Maintenance activities for Differential in RELAY system

body.raw:
# Differential

## Activities

1. Ratio/Phase Angle
2. Slope Characteristic
3. Harmonic Restraint
4. Insulation Resistance

2. Zone Timing
3. Directional
4. Polarization

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Insulation Resistance
